┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    DIJKSTRA'S ALGORITHM                      │
│                                                              │
│  1. Initialize: dist[source] = 0, dist[all others] = ∞      │
│  2. Priority Queue: insert source with priority 0           │
│                                                              │
│  3. Loop until queue is empty:                              │
│     a. Extract node U with MINIMUM distance                 │
│     b. For each neighbor V of U:                            │
