│     b. For each neighbor V of U:                            │
│        • candidate = dist[U] + weight(U → V)               │
│        • If candidate < dist[V]:                            │
│            - dist[V] = candidate                            │
│            - prev[V] = U   (for path reconstruction)        │
│            - Push V into priority queue                     │
│                                                              │
│  4. Result: dist[] contains shortest distances from source  │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

