## Complexity Summary

| Operation | Time | Space |
|-----------|------|-------|
| `get` | **O(1)** | — |
| `put` | **O(1)** | — |
| `peek` | O(1) | — |
| `keys` | O(n) | O(n) |
| **Overall** | — | **O(capacity)** |

> **Key insight:** Storing the `key` inside the node is what makes eviction O(1) — when the LRU node is removed from the list, we can immediately delete it from the HashMap without a reverse lookup.

